sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant PY   as Python Gateway
    participant CFG  as gateway.yaml
    participant MB   as Modbus Device
    participant FS   as core/settings/
    participant CERT as config/certs/
    participant C    as C Binary
    participant SRV  as 2030.5 Server

    Note over PY: __main__.py starts

    PY  ->> CFG: load GatewayConfig
    CFG -->> PY: host, port, cert paths, register maps

    PY  ->> CERT: validate device.pem + ca/
    CERT -->> PY: ok / ConfigError

    Note over PY,MB: read device state

    PY  ->> MB: connect (TCP :502)
    MB  -->> PY: connected

    loop for each ReadMap address
        PY  ->> MB: read_register(address)
        MB  -->> PY: value
    end
    Note over PY: build DERState

    PY  ->> FS: write_settings(DERState) → 4 XML files

    Note over PY,C: spawn C binary

    PY  ->> C: spawn(client_test --config gateway.yaml)

    C   ->> FS: read DERCapability/Settings/Status/Availability.xml
    FS  -->> C: XML content

    C   ->> CERT: load device.pem + CA bundle
    CERT -->> C: ECDSA P-256 keypair

    Note over C,SRV: 2030.5 resource discovery

    C   ->> SRV: GET /dcap
    SRV -->> C: DeviceCapability (edev URI, time URI)

    C   ->> SRV: GET /edev/{sfdi}
    SRV -->> C: EndDevice (fsa URI, der URI)

    C   ->> SRV: GET /edev/{sfdi}/fsa
    SRV -->> C: FunctionSetAssignments (derp URI)

    C   ->> SRV: GET /edev/{sfdi}/fsa/derp
    SRV -->> C: DERProgramList

    C   ->> SRV: GET /edev/{sfdi}/fsa/derp/{id}/derc
    SRV -->> C: DERControlList

    C   ->> SRV: PUT /edev/{sfdi}/der/1/dercap
    C   ->> SRV: PUT /edev/{sfdi}/der/1/ders
    C   ->> SRV: PUT /edev/{sfdi}/der/1/derst
    C   ->> SRV: PUT /edev/{sfdi}/der/1/dera

    C   ->> SRV: POST /edev/{sfdi}/fsa/derp/{id}/derc/sub
    SRV -->> C: 201 Created

    Note over C,PY: steady state

    SRV -->> C: DERControl notification
    C   ->> PY: EVENT_JSON: {type:start, mrid:..., control:{...}}
    Note over PY: bridge.apply() → write Modbus registers
